  "body": "# Worm's Eye View\n\nA simple [Better than Adventure](https://www.betterthanadventure.net/) mod that allows you to enable photo mode shaders outside of photo mode.\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/worms-eye-view/versions\"><img alt=\"Latest Release\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/release/FrostBird347/Worms-Eye-View?label=Latest%20Release\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/FrostBird347/Worms-Eye-View/issues\"><img alt=\"Open Issues\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/issues-raw/FrostBird347/Worms-Eye-View?label=Open%20Issues\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/FrostBird347/Worms-Eye-View\"><img alt=\"Github Repo\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Github%20Repo-%20?logo=github&color=%230d1117\"/></a>\n\n## Showcase\n\n<img alt=\"BTA 7.1 Photo Mode Shaders\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/FrostBird347/Worms-Eye-View/Main/media/showcase/Shaders.webp\"/>\n\nNote that the recording below was taken before the depth map was fixed for the `outline`, `outline2` and `distantblur` shaders.\n\n<video controls src=\"https://github.com/FrostBird347/Worms-Eye-View/assets/39435218/fe7fc76c-3370-4861-beef-f295a25b51d5\"></video>\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/72UN2aPCUYQ\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n",
